results.description:
White Rock lake, pool behind the lower spillway steps
Playing With Your Food
I watched this cormorant dive and come up with something that it was tossing in the air and then catching again.  I was not sure what it was until I processed the photos.  It looks like it was playing with a pecan.  I don't know if it ever actually swallowed it.  Love those blue eyes.
